::Prowl/Striker/Ramulus::

Walking toward the bridge, Prowl nearly crashes into Shadow Stalker. He looks 
at her in surprise, looking at Rhinox, at who she had her gun aimed.

"What's the problem?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Striker walks into the bridge, his eyes widening as he sees the damage.

"Slag! This is too much!" his scanner beeps, picking up the distress signal 
from a strange ship. He looks at the scanner. The ship was maximal!

"Ramulus, Smokescreen," he says into his comm-link, "A new ship has crashed. 
A maximal battle cruiser. I'm going to check it out. If you two can come 
along, it'd be great."

Having said that, he heads to the exit of the Ark.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus comes to a stop near the Ark, looking in surprise at the damage. He 
recieves the transmission from Striker.

"My presence is required elsewhere," he says to Longhunter, "You can come 
along if you want."
